{"tid":1703524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[1111] 少少嘅改變 可能為聽日帶來唔同嘅結果","createTime":"2019-11-10T10:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T13:24:32.000Z","uid":48443,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a6b1aaf3f7e153cedfee2c387b858e7333cbec","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"知道各位聽日各區集會準備得如火如荼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非可能未必知道可以點樣幫手，<br />\n我自己就有一個少少嘅建議。 <br />\n<br />\n聽日和理非無論想主動罷工被動罷工都好，<br />\n可唔可以一齊著黑色衫加口罩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好屌我住，聽日其實正正係blackbloc 最幫到手嘅一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲曱甴警聽日一定高度戒備，見黑色衫就想去咬，和理非黑色衫就算俾人查班曱甴都唔會咬到你，但係你分分鐘可以幫到勇武手足buy time，甚至令佢哋草木皆兵，更加容易犯錯。<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日鍾意被罷工好，點都好，和理非一定要著黑衫。勇武手足就當然彩虹戰衣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"47be32a1272b77fdb364ec001268b755727f8028","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"1111和理非黑色衫"},{"pid":"0be52642adb19d648446f604765775e256f992c9","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"出街嘅全部都要黑色衫"},{"pid":"a86b9775fc4f75acc30a6a479591dfd144084458","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"越多人著越安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cbb037cdc483a0de0c5f7e17ac4b476c392bd5","tid":1703524,"uid":124180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"全部人黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至少都比到同路人睇有幾人想被罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1688ed6465637f5811da886153855c92b716770","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"唔知要自推幾多次 但係要個個都見到"},{"pid":"a2aebcbcd23018fc30827415cac7f88e18b33658","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d81a87e906ce912d3b86dca0ddaa16b88c878d","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63cbb037cdc483a0de0c5f7e17ac4b476c392bd5","tid":1703524,"uid":124180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"全部人黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至少都比到同路人睇有幾人想被罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:19:55.000Z","msg":"就係咁樣"},{"pid":"7f900a96fcf2a2ca02a04278ead329020a009a6b","tid":1703524,"uid":87320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"好似好岩聽 推左先"},{"pid":"3bbc0b5dcd8b9a00f98df80070b41f2d400b948c","tid":1703524,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"大家一齊著"},{"pid":"18b136ceb997c7c701a1a37c9f9ae4f7e40c9c41","tid":1703524,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"幫推幫帶 11/11 黎明來到 物資綜合post<br />\n<a hre